{"tid":2136202,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"寫詩風/政府跟/像極了愛情","createTime":"2020-08-02T03:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T13:13:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6c1d30695beca351510fc983cb1f374bef3fd0dd","tid":2136202,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200802/YCMVYTXXN7SW3HLGKP4VO7ELVA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200802%2FYCMVYTXXN7SW3HLGKP4VO7ELVA%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnQmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=023a453d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200802%2FYCMVYTXXN7SW3HLGKP4VO7ELVA%2F&h=f1a61dc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200802/YCMVYTXXN7SW3HLGKP4VO7ELVA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n寫詩風/政府跟/像極了愛情<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「早上晴空萬里/下午卻下起了大雨/像極了愛情」，「點了美式咖啡不加冰/結果來了一杯熱的/像極了愛情」&hellip;&hellip;這些以「像極了愛情」作結尾的「詩」，近日在兩岸掀起風潮。網民發現詩中以「像極了愛情」五字作結，便能增添意境，連台灣政府也爭相仿效。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cKHW-19sFzbPviXgOcDjGrzeDWU=/640x883/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KNX26D4SXCAIH6ZFZ2CWLBN5EM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcKHW-19sFzbPviXgOcDjGrzeDWU%3D%2F640x883%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKNX26D4SXCAIH6ZFZ2CWLBN5EM.jpg&h=c566075a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n源自大陸歌手作品<br />\n<br />\n這場「像極了愛情」寫詩大賽，上周四（30日）登上台灣Google熱搜第一名。不但網民二次創作，連台灣內政部、財政部等也跟風。例如台灣上期開出史上最高獎金的威力彩，財政部公佈中獎名單時，便寫上「滿心期待兩個月一次的開獎/結果又是沒中/像極了愛情」。內政部宣傳違例停車時，則寫「強求卡位，吃虧的終究是自己/明明沒有位置，還要硬擠過來/像極了愛情」。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n知名導演蘇三毛近日分享一張「教你如何寫詩」的圖文（圖），隨意寫一段話，最後加上「像極了愛情」就變成一首詩。據報這份「秘笈」的原創者是一名物業管理的上班族。<br />\n<br />\n香。。。。。。。。。。。。。。不過因愛情內涵相當豐富，「像極了愛情」讓人在不同的語境中，都可將「愛情」作為喻體使用，讀者自然會去尋找愛情的其中一個內涵。<br />\n<br />\n台灣聯合新聞網"},{"pid":"50ca9779b5a8da2eef683df2592dec83c7125c91","tid":2136202,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T05:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6900c25d34f8e2b08eeca902a89570e4ff617a","tid":2136202,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:00:52.000Z","msg":"你你像極了愛情 今宵不冷靜"},{"pid":"c663635221621211a448a1c90174603917d80aee","tid":2136202,"uid":360830,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:03:37.000Z","msg":"其實將<br />\n一句句子斬開來寫<br />\n已經有<br />\n新詩的味道"},{"pid":"6ede68dbec16e276b0065f12048019887b50288e","tid":2136202,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c663635221621211a448a1c90174603917d80aee","tid":2136202,"uid":360830,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:03:37.000Z","msg":"其實將<br />\n一句句子斬開來寫<br />\n已經有<br />\n新詩的味道"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a4a9188c5a7353957e70edb9bcf18313bfda00","tid":2136202,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:04:59.000Z","msg":"什麼是情<br />\n什麼是愛"},{"pid":"f5d19877c28eaf01cef15bce3696f8317dea78d5","tid":2136202,"uid":272445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:51:35.000Z","msg":"被盲婚啞嫁<br />\n卻無法分手<br />\n像極了愛情"},{"pid":"e60f12eb4784fdcaaa22d010ebfbb9e3ee9b069b","tid":2136202,"uid":142247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7a4a9188c5a7353957e70edb9bcf18313bfda00","tid":2136202,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T06:04:59.000Z","msg":"什麼是情<br />\n什麼是愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T13:49:07.000Z","msg":"什麼叫做情<br />\n什麼叫做愛"},{"pid":"4b3b2672f5af087f7370e34aab8fd87700f8f934","tid":2136202,"uid":199709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:13:00.000Z","msg":"made in Chi na 不了 <br />\n拉"}]}